# Reset Regret Tracker Service
# Service to reset regret tracking and metrics

# Request
bool reset_reference            # Reset reference planner regret
bool reset_dynamic              # Reset dynamic regret
bool reset_safe                 # Reset safe regret
bool reset_metrics              # Reset all metrics

---
# Response
bool success                    # Success flag
string message                  # Status message
float64 cumulative_regret_before  # Cumulative regret before reset
float64 cumulative_regret_after   # Cumulative regret after reset
